Dependencies:

  g++ 4.4+
  libevent 1.4+
  python 3.1
  gdb           (for printing backtraces)

Build instructions:

  ./bootstrap.sh
  ./autogen.sh
  ./configure
  make all

Mac OS X prerequisites:

  - Install gcc46 from macports (http://www.macports.org)
  - Create config.mk at the top-level directory containing lines:
      CC  = gcc-mp-4.6
      CXX = g++-mp-4.6

